{"tid":551383,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"近千iPhone X用家投訴無法接聽電話　蘋果調查 (17:11)","createTime":"2018-02-05T15:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T09:11:47.000Z","uid":69289,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"83d7eb6d800a1a1dc99678f033a09a184372a0c7","tid":551383,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:01:30.000Z","msg":"電話最基本的功能，當然是在它鈴聲響起來時接聽，隔空與人談話。但截至2月4日，有逾800名用家於蘋果論壇上投訴，蘋果公司最新型號的智能手機iPhone X不能接聽電話。<br />\n<br />\n問世三個月的iPhone X，標榜利用人面辨識技術解鎖，用家於手上的裝置就可以體驗人工智能。但這部賣近8600港元的高科技智能電話，無法做到最基本的功能。<br />\n<br />\n有用家去年12月初在蘋果論壇上投訴，電話鈴聲響起後，iPhone X的屏幕最長延遲10秒才亮起，導致用家無法按鍵接聽來電。用家更指，即使重裝電話亦無法解決問題。有逾800名用家表示遇上同類問題，蘋果公司指，正對這些報告展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司的產品最近問題多多，公司早前確認小部分iPhone 7因底板上的一個零件出現問題，導致在信號良好的地方亦無法連接手機網絡，出現「沒有服務」情況，因而為iPhone 7推出免費維修計劃。去年12月，蘋果透過軟件更新修復macOS上的安全漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00005/1517821639624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00005%2F1517821639624&d=efTyPGwSmWvSIciG6hPrPZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0678dc14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180205%2Fs00005%2F1517821639624&h=7f75b517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180205/s00005/1517821639624</a>"},{"pid":"802fd409997dcc790cc546b7fd72eecaaef3204c","tid":551383,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"放心啦，就嚟停產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca06ed97b65c781a21e5733e7cbadf26e2759ecf","tid":551383,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"X真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477335d57485608f3856343323413ed41b82fa1d","tid":551383,"uid":20658,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"白老鼠係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"70049a14e8b31e5c808f27439c472f782135bd0d","tid":551383,"uid":13281,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"反而我係經常接左個電話<br />\n部iPhone又開始左通話計時<br />\n但係就聽唔倒對面講野<br />\n對面就話我冇接直接cut線冇通話計時<br />\n無數人試過無數次<br />\nRestore左之後都一樣會<br />\n已經習慣左人地打黎冇聲我就收線打返返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dff6d599472d1be5a4a08c1fa7b1981a7543804","tid":551383,"uid":96708,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"You're using it wrong"},{"pid":"c6184aee04875aa9f5656ba95a15d2d1f951f0f1","tid":551383,"uid":102542,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"隔離post仲有條柒頭話買8/8 plus唔買X正笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蘋果每次出新野買第二代是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb324157729ac6dec3a9839b2bf6a657c7be96a8","tid":551383,"uid":135390,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"玩緊某最近好多人玩既大陸槍game<br />\n有人打過黎既話就會lag到仆街<br />\n亦都聽唔到個電話,亦都打唔番比人地<br />\n仲話粒u好勁好勁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開得一隻game都搞到咁"},{"pid":"27dc9d7ffa88da5caef7471e61be8d374e0a8e69","tid":551383,"uid":15835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T18:16:09.000Z","msg":"香港無人有事，繼續用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080fedca2c078d23d46089679a4eb4e00d6cbe93","tid":551383,"uid":30808,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T23:00:53.000Z","msg":"買部電話返黎  冇得聽電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定係用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcee224c1e97f28f356911ef0386776402d183be","tid":551383,"uid":129835,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"cited